<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>83</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kwa wingi wa nyama,
 Na sadaka pia,
 Hupata wapi salama,
 Kwondoa hatia?

[V2]
 Sadaka ni Yesu,
 Hwondoa makosa;
 Dhabihu mwenye jina kuu,
 Atanitakasa.

[V3]
 Kwa yangu imani,
 Nikuweke sasa
 Mkono mwako kichwani
 Kukiri makosa.

[V4]
 Roho yakumbuka
 Mambo ya mtini,
 Mzigo ulijitweka,
 Ndiyo yangu deni.

[V5]
 Deni hutanguka,
 Tukimuamini;
 Kwa damu tumeokoka,
 Twimbe furahani.</lyrics>
<title>Kwa Wingi Wa Nyama TZR83</title>
</song>